<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Rebeja (Posts about Azure)</title><link>https://rebeja.eu/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://rebeja.eu/categories/azure.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><copyright>Contents Â© 2018 &lt;a href="mailto:petru.rebeja@gmail.com"&gt;Petru Rebeja&lt;/a&gt; </copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 28 Dec 2018 14:44:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Adding Disqus comments to Ghost blog on Azure</title><link>https://rebeja.eu/posts/adding-disqus-comments-to-ghost-blog-on-azure/</link><dc:creator>Petru Rebeja</dc:creator><description>&lt;p&gt;
If you have a &lt;a href="https://ghost.org/"&gt;Ghost&lt;/a&gt; hosted on &lt;a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/"&gt;Azure&lt;/a&gt; (like I did) then you may want to add &lt;a href="https://disqus.com/"&gt;Disqus&lt;/a&gt; comments to it (like I did).
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
To do so, follow the steps below:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol class="org-ol"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://disqus.com/profile/signup/"&gt;Create a Disqus account&lt;/a&gt; if you haven't done so already.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://disqus.com/profile/login/"&gt;Login to Disqus&lt;/a&gt; and navigate to the admin page.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click on &lt;a href="https://disqus.com/profile/login/?next=/admin/install/"&gt;Install Disqus&lt;/a&gt; and choose &lt;a href="https://disqus.com/admin/install/platforms/ghost/"&gt;Ghost&lt;/a&gt; from the list.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open a new tab and navigate to &lt;a href="https://portal.azure.com/"&gt;Azure portal&lt;/a&gt; and from the dashboard open/navigate to the application hosting your Ghost blog.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;On the application blade select &lt;code&gt;App Service Editor&lt;/code&gt; and press &lt;code&gt;Go-&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; to open the editor for your blog.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In the editor navigate to &lt;code&gt;wwwroot\content\themes\&amp;lt;your-theme&amp;gt;\post.hbs&lt;/code&gt;. This will load the file in the panel on the right.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Go back to &lt;a href="https://disqus.com/admin/install/platforms/ghost/"&gt;Ghost Install Instructions&lt;/a&gt; on Disqus and copy the &lt;a href="https://disqus.com/admin/install/platforms/universalcode/"&gt;Universal Embed Code&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paste the code into post.hbs file in the place where you want your comment section to be.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find the section to define configuration variables and make it look like this:
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kd"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;disqus_config&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kd"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="k"&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;page&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;url&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s1"&gt;'{{@blog.url}}{{url}}'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="k"&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;page&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;identifier&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s1"&gt;'{{id}}'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="p"&gt;};&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Happy blogging!
